    .col-lg-4
      %img.img-circle{:alt => "140x140", "data-src" => "holder.js/140x140", :src => "data:image/png;base64,", :style => "width: 140px; height: 140px;"}
        %h2 記錄生活消費
        %p 不論是Android 或是 iPhone 用戶都可以透過AndroMoney手機APP, 輕鬆地記錄下每一筆花費，轉帳，收入與支出

    / /.col-lg-4
    .col-lg-4
